{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aba9bb08cc","title":"给蓝公武\"的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8e835ac7f4","index":0,"year":1948,"month":4,"day":27,"articleId":"aba9bb08cc"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji24.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji24":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"41a0b1ffe2","type":"paragraph","text":"给蓝公武\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"aba9bb08cc"},{"id":"5312eaf94a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年4月27日）公武先生三十年前，拜读先生在《晨报》及《国民公报》上的崇论宏议，现闻先生居所距此不远，甚思一唔，借验教益。兹派车迎候简蒙拨元杠驾，无任欢迎数颂大安","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"aba9bb08cc"},{"id":"14cf71ff35","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"aba9bb08cc"},{"id":"3c717cf522","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四八年四月廿七日，于陈南庄[I]蓝公线（1887-1957），江苏吴江人。长期从事新闻工作。1945年秋到运青察翼解放区，先后任察哈尔省政府教育厅厅长、华北人民政府副主籍等职。新中国成立后，曾任最高人民检察署副检察长。1957年资世，根指他临络前的申请，中共中央认他为中国共产党党员。武先中","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"aba9bb08cc"},{"id":"4a28ba754d","type":"paragraph","text":"大","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"aba9bb08cc"},{"id":"792ca9c193","type":"paragraph","text":"三海所指送地生限上家在装展，了州人时那此不是，基四一名，转取教三。我汉我也属传景钱元超金发在教心。旅戏大店","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"aba9bb08cc"},{"id":"76a1bbbf13","type":"paragraph","text":"无清东小半侧机样法有店毛泽东致蓝公武信的手稿","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"aba9bb08cc"}],"page":{"id":"9b771601d9","publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"aba9bb08cc","start":237,"end":238}}}},"__N_SSG":true}